r(s)</em>: Todd Adkins, Brad Lomenick. <em>Type</em>: Video. <em>Level</em>: Introductory. <em>Length</em>: 6 minutes.<strong></strong></li>             <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tdrh6I0RtPU"><strong>Ending a Mentoring Relationship.</strong></a><em> Year Developed</em>: 2010. <em>Source</em>: theRBPgroup. <em>Presenter(s)</em>: Mike Taylor. <em>Type</em>: Video. <em>Level</em>: Introductory. <em>Length</em>: 1 minute.<strong></strong></li>             <li><a href="https://www.ellevatenetwork.com/jam-sessions/5751-understanding-the-impact-of-mentorship-as-a-tool-for-leaders"><strong>Understanding the Impact of Mentorship as a Tool for Leaders.</strong></a><em> Year Developed</em>: 2010. <em>Source</em>: Ellevate. <em>Presenter(s)</em>: Rachel Barrett Cooke. <em>Type</em>: Webinar. <em>Level</em>: Introductory. <em>Length</em>: 37 minutes.<strong></strong></li>             <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dlecg_DorxQ"><strong>Concluding the Mentee-Mentor Relationship.</strong></a><em> Year Developed</em>: 2018. <em>Source</em>: American Society of Nephrology. <em>Presenter(s)</em>: Unknown. <em>Type</em>: Video. <em>Level</em>: Introductory. <em>Length</em>: 3 minutes.</li>           </ul>           </div>               <hr /><p><strong>References</strong></p><ol>  <li>Sujata, B., Oliveras, E., and Edson, W.N. (2001). <em>How Can Self-Assessment Improve the Quality of Healthcare? </em> Operations Research Issue Paper 2(4). Published for the U.S. Agency for International Development (USAID) by the Quality Assurance (QA) Project.</li>  <li>MCH Leadership Competencies Workgroup (2018), &quot;<a href="https://mchb.hrsa.gov/training/leadership-00.asp">MCH Leadership Competencies Version 4.0</a>&quot;.</li>  <li>The Center for Health Leadership and Practice, a Center of the Public Health Institute. (2003). &ldquo;<a href="https://rackham.umich.edu/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/MORE-faculty-mentoring-handbook.pdf">Mentoring Guide: A Gu